  <description>
    <p>
      An unofficial WhatsApp desktop application for Linux.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Features come with whatsapp web</li>
      <li>System tray icon</li>
      <li>Icon in systray with different icon if there is new messages</li>
      <li>Fullscreen mode</li>
      <li>background running</li>
    </ul>

    <p>What doesn't include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Video calls</li>
      <li>On-call calls</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
